v1.2.3 round-27 (2026.7.19) — First-principles review + manual mockup fix:
  - Version: versionCode=123, versionName="1.2.3" (unchanged — review round).
  - ui-gameflow.js (GPL v3): Fixed misleading comment in _onGameClockExpired
    about isDeadPosition semantics — now accurately describes that
    isDeadPosition checks whether checkmate is possible by any sequence of
    legal moves (FIDE 5.2.2), which is exactly the FIDE 6.9 condition.
  - ai-bridge.js (GPL v3): Removed redundant `if(_gameOverStatusKey==='timeout')
    return '1/2-1/2'` branch in _deriveGameResult — the fallback already
