This directory contains the JavaScript source modules for the chess UI.
These modules are merged by build-chess.py into chess.html.

v1.2.0 Phase 82+++ (2026.7.12, same-version deep refactor):
  - Version remains versionCode=120, versionName="1.2.0".
  - ui.js (GPL v3): Phase 82+++ — extracted 3 more rendering blocks from
    renderInternal() (476 lines) into dedicated functions:
    _renderAIBar(h, oppC) — AI opponent bar (.pbar#ai-bar) with icon, name,
      level, clock, waiting/thinking indicators, captured pieces (split at 7),
      engine search info (#ai-search-info), ponder info (#ai-ponder-info).
      oppC passed as param.
    _renderPlayerBar(h) — quick toolbar (.qtoolbar with undo/redo/flip/hint/
      control-map, hidden in review/setup) + player bar (.pbar#player-bar with
      icon, clickable name, clock, captured pieces, your-turn, resign).
    _renderInfoBars(h) — three optional info bars: tablebase status (≤7 pieces),
      ECO opening recommendation (_ecoEnabled, not Chess960), AI hint area
      (isHintLoading/hintText) with MultiPV alternative lines.
    renderInternal: 476→359 lines (−117). Cumulative reduction: 1,365→359
    (−1,006 lines, −74%). All extracted functions use the h string
    concatenation pattern (receive h, return h).
  - No new modules; build-order unchanged (13 modules). Re-run python3 build-chess.py.

v1.2.0 Phase 82++ (2026.7.12, same-version deep refactor):
  - Version remains versionCode=120, versionName="1.2.0".
