    block from renderInternal() (615 lines) into a new _renderReviewMode(h)
    function. The block renders the complete review-mode overlay: review board
    (with coordinate labels, control map, visual annotations, SVG arrows),
    eval bar, move slider, eval trend chart, navigation buttons, analyze-all
